From: conda-forge <conda-forge@example.com>
Date: Sun, 06 Apr 2025 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Remove bundled googletest submodule from 3rdparty

The GitHub archive tarball does not include git submodules, so
3rdparty/googletest is an empty directory. Remove the add_subdirectory
call; the find_package(GTest) call is added to tests/CMakeLists.txt
in a separate patch.
---
 3rdparty/CMakeLists.txt | 6 ------
 1 file changed, 6 deletions(-)

diff --git a/3rdparty/CMakeLists.txt b/3rdparty/CMakeLists.txt
index 1111111..2222222 100644
--- a/3rdparty/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/3rdparty/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -26,11 +26,5 @@ set(CMAKE_POSITION_INDEPENDENT_CODE on)

 # GoogleTest -----------------------------
-set(INSTALL_GTEST off)
-set(BUILD_GMOCK on)
-set(CMAKE_POLICY_DEFAULT_CMP0077 NEW)
-if(BUILD_TESTS)
-    add_subdirectory(googletest)
-endif()

 # pybind11 -----------------------------
